social_posts.post_text: Wish trailer is here! We have been pouring our hearts into this film everyday and we’re pumped you finally get to see the glimpse of the music, magic, and the watercolor look we have been geeking out about. Starring @arianadebose Chris Pine @alantudyk. Music by @juliamichaels x @thebenjaminrice Only in theaters this November✨

Everyday I feel lucky I get to be her mom. Happy Mother’s Day to mothers, mother figures, and army of cool aunts out there. We love you! Swipe to enjoy my daughter’s current assessment of our height comparison. 
.
.
.
#mothersday #colorpencil #traditionalart #sketch #sketchbook

Our new Wish posters drop today! @arianadebose as Asha x Chris Pine as Magnifico. 

All the Barbenheimers heading to theaters this weekend can check these out in all their extra large printed glory. We are in our final stretch of finishing this film and I am in awe of the amazing talents from all the departments at @disneyanimation every single day.

So it begins, our Wish North American footage tour kicks off in the beautiful city of Toronto. Super proud to show off our crew’s beautiful work in the extended 20 minutes footage from Wish. It’s my first press tour ever and it was so much fun! Huge thank you to the lovely team  at @disneystudioscanada ! See you all in theaters November 22nd ❤️
#disney #disneywishmovie #toronto #animation

Magical first day on the scoring stage for Wish. Can’t wait for you all to hear what our composer Dave Metzger have been up to! 

Thank you @oh.deer.me.art for making us a little crochet Star to bring on this adventure⭐️
.
.
.
@disneywishmovie #disneywish #disneyanimation #filmscore #soundstage

Come out this Sunday at @gallerynucleus for the Art For Maui show. I will have this original watercolor painting there along with the work from many lovely artists. The gallery opens at 3pm for one evening-in person only. Thank you @davidd.au for curating and organizing this benefit art show!

All the purchase of the artwork will be donated directly to Maui Strong Fund.
.
.
.
#artformaui #gallerynucleus #galleryshow #watercolorpainting #originalpainting #traditionalart

I took Kina to join us in DCI today (Digital Cut In-when we approve a group of final shots for the film) I took this photo as she walked down the main hall at @disneyanimation to the theater with Chris, @jupajones, Jim, and Albert. She rated all of 25 DCI shots she saw today from @disneywishmovie as “excellent!”

Swipe to see a video from 4 years ago when she still thought Elsa lived in this building and sang Let It Go in the loading dock in honor of her favorite queen.

#disneyanimation #disneywish #behindthescenes #elsa

New WISH trailer is here✨One of the joy of being back to work in the studios is that I get to see every shot of WISH in the theater (and also in EDR and HDR-now I know what the differences are 👀) 

We got to show selected sequences for our press kick offs at the historic El Capitan theater last week and I love seeing the beautiful delicate paper texture, line work and colors on the widest screen yet. Shout out to Art and VFX combining their super powers and being fearless on this new journey together.

This week we continue our days of sitting in the dark dark room for hours to finish our color timing (a process to put a finishing touch on final colors) and it will all be very worth it comes November 22! 

@disneywishmovie #wish #wishmovie2023 #disneyanimation #animation #behindthescenes #story

We wrapped our final sound mixing and @disneywishmovie is ready for the world. I have never witnessed this level of precisions in sounds. Watching @defmxr and his team worked gave me a new appreciation of this art form.  Hearing the scores and the songs in @dolbytheatre Atmos is 🔥

What an absolute joy to tell a story about the sparks that keep our dreams alive. In addition to that, I get to collaborate with so many amazing & talented friends (shout out to you @disneyanimation & @arianadebose @juliamichaels @thebenjaminrice) to make WISH a reality. This week, the film comes out into the world. To say that I am freaking excited (!!!) is beyond an understatement. And it got me reflecting on the journey leading up to this. I have always been someone who love celebrating small moments. But this week makes me thankful for all the struggles it took to get here, too. Those days allowed me to grow and discover many things I didn’t know I could do. And often, I also found people who were willing to help (as there are many forms of Star out there.) 

Much like the journey of Asha, knowing what your wish is—is only the start of an exciting journey ahead. 
.
.
.
@disneywishmovie #disney #disneywish #animation #traditionaldrawing #wish

Thank you @goldenglobes for this recognition for our film! It means a lot to all our cast and crew @disneyanimation who pour their hearts into this film. We came together to tell a story about how wondrous things can happen when you take ownership and action towards your dream. Beyond grateful for this nomination!!! กรี๊ด🥰

.

#goldenglobes #goldenglobes2024 #animatedmovie #awardseason

Grateful for this recognition from @criticschoice !!! So proud of our cast and crew for this film and for the incredible songs by @juliamichaels and @thebenjaminrice beautifully performed by @arianadebose✨So much love (and a lot of sweat in sweatbox) going into every shot of this film. Congrats @disneyanimation !
.
.

#criticschoiceawards #nomination @disneywishmovie #wish #wishmovie

Starting a new sketchbook is always daunting to me. I got over the fear eventually but it took a month of this sketchbook just sitting in my backpack. I love the color of this soft cover moleskine. 
.
.
.
#colerase #prismacolor #moleskine #sketchbook #chubbycat

When we went to Japan, @disneystudiojp asked if I would like to draw for @ikutaerika.official 🥰 Of course, an Asha for Asha. I drew this with the same pencil I used for the sketchbook drawings in the film. Time lapse video on @disneystudiojp IG. Thank you so much Japan for a warm welcome for @disneywishmovie ✨
.
.

#disneywish #drawings #japantrip #presstour #ikutaerika #asha #japan

Kina caught me drawing her and asked if she could color herself. I have drawn in her sketchbook before, so it was only fair that I shared mine this time. 
.

Love the energy of this incredible animation community as we all had blast at the @goldenglobes together. The wide range of storytelling and visual styles from all the nominees this year really give me so much excitement for the future of animation. Super proud to be representing @disneywishmovie & @disneyanimation And big congratulations to The Boy and the Heron crew!

Side note#1: I texted this photo to @ryangreenart who quickly sent me back the second pic😂

Side note#2: A couple weeks ago, I was stressed out on what to wear and had considered renting a tux. But I’m glad @benjaminholtrop and the glam team swooped in to the rescue. Photos incoming in the next post:)

📸 by @phillordy
